  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=hnok2uvc1r]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hnok2uvc1r]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759481157695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619741326/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759481157695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1065\" data-width=\"1894\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413790\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"273c54f8-adc6-4993-9676-647f1ec6e98e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759481157695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759481157695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>While we don&rsquo;t use a PBR Metallic workflow at Pixar, it remains a fairly typical workflow among artists, whether you&rsquo;re using PBR maps from an online material library or texturing software like Substance Painter.  Luckily, RenderMan ships with a handy node called <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224201\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrMetallicWorkflow</a>, which can be easily used with your PBR maps and a PxrSurface.</p><p>This lesson will guide you through the process.</p><p>The maps used in this lesson were kindly provided by our rendering friends at <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://greyscalegorilla.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Greyscalegorilla</a>, and the example used is Copper Corroded Heavy 01</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759485298191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619741326/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759485298191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"636\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619479303\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"ec1ef2fc-82f0-41d6-9668-31e9663dc7b4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759485298191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=636 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759485298191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377 1x\" /></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"0f42440a-787e-4834-855d-ecb9270571c2\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>As the Eagle model doesn&rsquo;t have any UVs, we&rsquo;re using a triplanar approach to mapping the textures onto the model via the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224293\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrMultiTexture </a>node</p><p>If your model has UVs, you can use a <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225070\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrTexture </a>node instead of the PxrMultiTexture node.</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"metallicworkflow_setup.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/metallicworkflow_setup.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759486708872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=433\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619741326/metallicworkflow_setup.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759486708872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"880\" data-width=\"1542\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413806\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"metallicworkflow_setup.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"7bee2351-670c-446a-ae3d-72b024bded60\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/metallicworkflow_setup.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759486708872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=866 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/metallicworkflow_setup.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759486708872&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=433 1x\" /></span><p>The setup is as follows:</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Create a PxrSurface</p></li><li><p>Create a PxrMetallicWorkflow node</p></li><li><p>Connect the <em>resultdiffuse </em>from the PxrMetallicWorkflow to the PxrSurface <em>diffusecolor</em></p></li><li><p>Use a PxrTexture for the diffuse map (or in this case a PxrMultiTexture node)</p></li><li><p>Connect the diffuse texture to the <em>basecolor </em>input of the PxrMetallicWorkflow node.</p></li><li><p>Load the Metallic texture map.</p></li><li><p>Connect the <em>resultr</em> from the metallic map into the <em>metallic </em>input of the PxrMetallicWorkflow node.</p></li><li><p>Connect the resultSpecularEdgeRGB from the PxrMetallicWorkflow into the specularEdgeColor of the PxrSurface.</p></li><li><p>Connect the resultSpecularFaceRGB from the PxrMetallicWorkflow into the specularFaceColor of the PxrSurface.</p></li><li><p>Load a Roughness map.</p></li><li><p>Connect the <em>resultr</em> from the roughness map into the <em>specularRoughness </em>input of the PxrSurface</p></li><li><p>Load your Normal map using a PxrNormalMap node.</p></li><li><p>Connect the <em>resultN </em>from the PxrNormalMap node into the <em>bumpNormal </em>input of the PxrSurface.</p></li><li><p>Hit Render and bathe in the PBR glory!</p></li></ol><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Eagle_Close_1.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488018969&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619741326/Eagle_Close_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488018969&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619446589\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Eagle_Close_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"95123c9e-ae1d-4375-a6de-927381b35a21\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488018969&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=712 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488018969&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Eagle_Close_3.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488028535&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619741326/Eagle_Close_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488028535&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619512067\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Eagle_Close_3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"b5ed7abd-31bd-4a67-bbce-d5d40122fd34\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488028535&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=712 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488028535&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Eagle_Close_2.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488023833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619741326/Eagle_Close_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488023833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619446595\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Eagle_Close_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"0f6feb62-939a-4e41-b7fd-1cdea45e2413\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488023833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=712 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488023833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Eagle_Close_4.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488032990&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619741326/Eagle_Close_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488032990&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619446601\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Eagle_Close_4.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"ce7d7d58-ca84-4c60-9038-60b587c82b4d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488032990&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=712&amp;height=712 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619741326/Eagle_Close_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759488032990&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h3 id=\"PxrSurface-MetallicWorkflow-FurtherRefinements\"><span data-colorid=\"hnok2uvc1r\">Further Refinements</span></h3><ul><li><p>In the example above, I also used a Houdini Dust HDA called EasyDust from <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://timotheemaron.gumroad.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>Timothee Maron</u></a></p></li><li><p>Use a PxrRemap, PxrThreshold, or PxrSplineMap node to correct the roughness map to your lookdev needs</p></li></ul><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  },
